00:54:03.800 --> 00:54:09.460
If I lose my password,
if a bank sometimes get--

00:54:09.460 --> 00:54:12.850
somehow gets hacked, there's
a way to backdoor and protect

00:54:12.850 --> 00:54:13.960
against the loss.

