01:01:47.470 --> 01:01:51.240
And any of you that have
studied a little bit about macro

01:01:51.240 --> 01:01:53.720
economics and you know
the velocity of money,

01:01:53.720 --> 01:01:58.010
it's how many times a piece
of currency turns over.

01:01:58.010 --> 01:02:02.330
It's sort of the economy divided
by the monetary base, whatever

01:02:02.330 --> 01:02:04.170
