01:05:36.240 --> 01:05:38.700
If you find a pain
point around privacy,

01:05:38.700 --> 01:05:41.810
a pain point around censorship--

01:05:41.810 --> 01:05:44.000
it depends on what
the pain point is,

01:05:44.000 --> 01:05:47.300
or if you're just something
