when you get to illiquids,

01:09:45.710 --> 01:09:47.569
is it really going
to create liquidity

01:09:47.569 --> 01:09:49.700
where there isn't liquidity?

01:09:49.700 --> 01:09:54.610
Real estate is still
very idiosyncratic.

01:09:54.610 --> 01:09:57.920
Gold is very fungible.

01:09:57.920 --> 01:10:04.120
Gold is something
that doesn't degrade.

01:10:04.120 --> 01:10:05.980
It could be in a warehouse.

01:10:05.980 --> 01:10:09.880
